text: Denise Yabut-Cojuangco (born 1 August 1961) is an equestrienne from the Philippines. Cojuangco represented the country in show jumping in the 1992 and 1996 Summer Olympics.Denise Cojuangco, Sports Reference LLC, Retrieved March 18, 2009. == References == Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Filipino female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of the Philippines Category:Cojuangco family Category:People from Makati Category:Sportspeople from Metro Manila Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics
